      • execMoveCheat

        public void execMoveCheat​(java.lang.String cheat,
                          Player cheatingPlayer)
        This method performs the actions needed for a move cheat. Only executed when cheats on server are activated.
        Parameters:
        cheat - The actual cheat (in this case 'move') plus the corresponding x - and y - coordinate that the player wants his robot to move to.
        cheatingPlayer - The player that activated this cheat.

      • execTurnCheat

        public void execTurnCheat​(java.lang.String cheat,
                          Player cheatingPlayer)
        This method performs the actions needed for a turn cheat. Only executed when cheats on server are activated.
        Parameters:
        cheat - The actual cheat (in this case 'turn') plus the desired direction the player wants his robot to be turned.
        cheatingPlayer - The player that activated this cheat.

      • execPlayCheat

        public void execPlayCheat​(java.lang.String cheat,
                          Player cheatingPlayer)
        This method performs the actions needed for a play card cheat. Only executed when cheats on server are activated.
        Parameters:
        cheat - The actual cheat (in this case 'play') plus the desired card that the player wants to play.
        cheatingPlayer - The player that activated this cheat.
